'use strict';
angular.module(moduleCore).provider('Env', function() {
  var _api_root, _dev, _seed;
  _dev = false;
  _seed = {};
  _api_root = '/api';
  return {
    setDev: function(d) {
      _dev = !!d;
      return this;
    },
    setApiRoot: function(api) {
      _api_root = api;
      return this;
    },
    setSeed: function(key, value) {
      _seed[key] = _.clone(value);
      return this;
    },
    $get: function() {
      return {
        dev: function() {
          return _dev;
        },
        seed: function(key) {
          if (_seed[key] != null) {
            return _seed[key];
          } else {
            return null;
          }
        },
        apiRoot: function() {
          return _api_root;
        }
      };
    }
  };
});
